Shank's Take:
Out of all the idiots in that group, I'd at least have to give Fenwick the award of "Least Hated." Hard to make enemies if you barely do anything, but that's great for all I care. If only he'd break himself free from the chains of that gaggle of morons.

Dagger's Take:
The cat? Can't stand em. True warriors fight for what they believe in! I enjoy fighting enemies I can respect, but I have no respect for people who don't care. I also think I might have allergies...
